Great Southern Bancorp votes stock split . Great Southern Bancorp Inc said Thursday its directors voted a two - for - one stock split . The stock split requires approval by a majority of the company ' s shareholders of a proposal to increase authorized shares to 20 million from 10 million . Shareholders will vote on the proposal at an October 16 , 1996 annual meeting . If approved , the stock split will be effective October 21 , record October 11 . Great Southern Bancorp has about $ 670 million in assets . Chicago newsdesk 312 408 8787 
